give its name ansible and path /usr/bin

2) INSTALL TERRAFORM PLUGIN
  GO IN TOOLS SECTION AND CONFIGURE IF YOU WANT TO NOT NECCESSARY BECAUSE I HAVE GIVEN IN CODE DIRECTLY

